Tragedy struck in Modakeke community of Osun State on Saturday night when an aged woman, identified as Mrs Kolade Omolayo was burnt to death as fire razed a building located on Alapata Street in the ancient town. A credible source informed the Tribune Online that the fire emanated from the late woman’s room. The woman’s lantern which was filled with kerosene spilt its contents on the floor. ALSO READ: Seven persons escape death in Onitsha gas explosion Her mattress got soaked by the kerosene in the process. Responsibility of the Church Why ethics remain crucial in a challenged economy —experts Osinbajo, Sanwoolu laud Airtel on CSR initiative New tax regime will put Nigerian consumers at the receiving… The deceased was said to have ignorantly struck a match, which led to fire incident that gutted the entire building. It took the intervention of Osun State Fire Service Station at Lagere, Ile-Ife, Obafemi Awolowo University (OAU), Ile-Ife Fire Service Station and residents of the area to put out the fire. The aged woman was burnt to ashes while her remains have been gathered for burial. Tribune Online gathered that two aged men survived the fire incident. When contacted, the administrative officer of the Osun State Fire Service, Mr Fatai Aremu, confirmed the incident. He said a quick response by men of the fire service in Lagere, Ile-Ife and OAU fire fighting unit aided the quenching of the raging fire. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY CURED NATURALLY IN 2 WEEKS FOR BIGGER, LONGER, HARDER SEXIER SEX WITH NEW MAN MACHINE